2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Gioi_thieu_ve_bo_mon_uno_cuc_dinh\"><\/span><b>Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n uno c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec9nh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e2y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng y\u00eau th\u00edch. B\u1ed9 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00f3 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong c\u00e1c d\u1ecbp t\u1ee5 t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed. D\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n, nh\u1edd v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i uno \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u00e1c m\u1ee9c ti\u1ec1n ph\u1ea1t d\u1ef1a theo th\u1eafng thua khi ch\u01a1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5153\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5153\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5153 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-1.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u00f4i n\u00e9t v\u1ec1 b\u00e0i uno\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-1.jpg?v=1736687004 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-1-300x150.jpg?v=1736687004 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-1-768x384.jpg?v=1736687004 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5153\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u00f4i n\u00e9t v\u1ec1 b\u00e0i uno<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, sau khi <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn h\u00f3a, vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u0169ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f4ng h\u01a1n. D\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n, b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed sinh l\u1eddi t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n game b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c. N\u1ebfu v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a qu\u00e1 r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed tham gia, anh em h\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o ngay c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 uno nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chi_tiet_ve_cach_choi_bai_uno_ai_cung_can_biet\"><\/span><b>Chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno ai c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 nghe \u0111\u1ebfn <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn ngay b\u1ed9 b\u00e0i t\u00e2y 52 con v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1eady, b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan hay c\u00f3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 n\u00e0o v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n casino. \u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n, c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd cho anh em m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn r\u00f5 nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bo_bai_uno_va_cach_chia\"><\/span><b>B\u1ed9 b\u00e0i uno v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch chia<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y qua b\u1ed9 b\u00e0i uno, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n anh em s\u1ebd \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1eaft m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i. M\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 b\u00e0i uno s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 108 l\u00e1 v\u1edbi 4 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc xanh l\u00e1, xanh d\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecf. Vi\u1ec7c n\u1eafm r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 b\u00e0i n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong<\/span><b> c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5152\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5152\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5152 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-2.jpg\" alt=\"S\u01a1 l\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch chia b\u00e0i\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-2.jpg?v=1736686978 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-2-300x150.jpg?v=1736686978 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-2-768x384.jpg?v=1736686978 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5152\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u01a1 l\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch chia b\u00e0i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e1n b\u00e0i, m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t 7 l\u00e1, s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh b\u1ed1c b\u00e0i trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i. S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn uno s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 n\u01a1i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i theo \u0111\u00f4i, c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 b\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd chia th\u00e0nh hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eafng th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_la_bai_trong_uno\"><\/span><b>Nh\u1eefng l\u00e1 b\u00e0i trong uno<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm r\u00f5 c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang th\u00ec m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Draw 2 cards: T\u1ea5m b\u00e0i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed1n m\u00e0u, n\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00e1 b\u00e0i n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat th\u00eam hai l\u00e1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Draw 4 cards: L\u00e1 b\u00e0i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng quy \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111i l\u00e1 b\u00e0i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u theo \u00fd th\u00edch v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c 4 l\u00e1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i s\u1ed1: M\u1ed7i m\u00e0u b\u00e0i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1c l\u00e1 t\u1eeb 0 \u0111\u1ebfn 9, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00e1 b\u00e0i c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Skip Cards: \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00e1 b\u00e0i m\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3t, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 4 m\u00e0u. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111i l\u00e1 b\u00e0i n\u00e0y th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reverse Cards: Khi ra l\u00e1 b\u00e0i n\u00e0y, v\u00f2ng ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, l\u00e1 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed1n m\u00e0u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Wild Cards: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e1 b\u00e0i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u theo \u00fd mu\u1ed1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5151\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5151\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5151 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-3.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u00e1 b\u00e0i c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft trong uno\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-3.jpg?v=1736686951 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-3-300x150.jpg?v=1736686951 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-3-768x384.jpg?v=1736686951 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5151\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u1eefng l\u00e1 b\u00e0i c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft trong uno<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Luat_choi_uno\"><\/span><b>Lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i uno<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi chia b\u00e0i xong, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e1t b\u00e0i s\u1ebd r\u00fat th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u00e1 ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean trong x\u1ea5p b\u00e0i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lu\u1eadt ban \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 m\u00e0u v\u00e0 con s\u1ed1. Sau \u0111\u00f3, <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh theo chi\u1ec1u kim \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 theo quy t\u1eafc c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng m\u00e0u ho\u1eb7c c\u00f9ng s\u1ed1: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u1ea7n ra nh\u1eefng l\u00e1 b\u00e0i c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng m\u00e0u ho\u1eb7c c\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi l\u00e1 b\u00e0i l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">R\u00fat b\u00e0i: Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00e1 b\u00e0i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p th\u00ec theo <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u00e1. N\u1ebfu l\u00e0 b\u00e0i b\u1ea1n v\u1eeba r\u00fat \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n th\u00ec v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ngay.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u00f9ng b\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t: Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng l\u00e1 b\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf tr\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng ch\u00fang \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u khi c\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5150\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5150\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5150 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-4.jpg\" alt=\"Lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a uno\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-4.jpg?v=1736686925 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-4-300x150.jpg?v=1736686925 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-uno-4-768x384.jpg?v=1736686925 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5150\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a uno<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu m\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y th\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u anh em s\u1ebd cho\u00e1ng ng\u1ee3p b\u1edfi c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00e1 b\u00e0i trong m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9. H\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a SV368 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i uno t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u n\u01a1i tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. B\u1ed9 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh board game \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111a d\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i tham gia. T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ngay c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh cao th\u1ee7 uno v\u00e0 chinh [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5153,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[117],"class_list":["post-5149","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc","tag-cach-choi-bai-uno"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5149","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5149"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5149\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5976,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5149\/revisions\/5976"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5153"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5149"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=5149"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=5149"}],"curies":[{"n